 their orbital parameters (such as Kozai-Lidov oscillations),\nrather than from a different initial condition or evolution between HSs and\nbinaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2023 11:40:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-15"}
